generated_description: maorika, legally known as reitz natura gmbh, is a company based in hamburg, germany, specializing in the distribution of certified manuka honey. the company imports manuka honey in food-grade 300 kg barrels from new zealand and subsequently fills it into high-quality, lightproof glass containers in germany. maorika's products are certified by independent laboratories for factors such as enzyme activity, pollen, pesticides, and methylglyoxal (mgo). the company emphasizes environmental sustainability by using glass packaging instead of plastic, ensuring the integrity and quality of its products.
